cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper proposes an algorithm for real-time 6DOF pose tracking of rigid 3D objects using a monocular RGB camera, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also proposes a novel dataset for monocular object pose tracking, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed approach in cluttered scenes, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) category.
